	margin-left: 0;

  color: $brand-info;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 18px;

}

.panel-primary > .panel-heading {

    border-bottom: 4px solid $brand-primary;

body .padding-top {

}

header nav.navbar-inverse {

}

color: #fff;

.btn-default:hover,
.btn-default:active,

	background-color: lighten($brand-primary,10%);
}

.sp-tagline-color {
	text-shadow: 0px 0px 20px #000;
}
